data.description: Beautiful Historic Home on Western Avenue! This Victorian era home on a fenced corner lot features lovely details throughout, including vestibule entry, grand staircase, built-in storage options, and solid wood trim and doors throughout. The spacious living room offers wood burning fireplace, bay window with seating, and two solid wood panel pocket doors that open up to parlor and formal dining room. Kitchen is well appointed with crisp white cabinetry, tile backsplash, and ceramic flooring. Upstairs, you'll find four spacious bedrooms with ample storage. Third floor is accessed by full staircase and has potential to easily be converted to additional living space. The basement level offers an additional 1,171 square feet, including a "speakeasy" style bar room! Recently replaced front porch with ceiling fan is the perfect place to sit back and take in all of the activity of this historic neighborhood. Call today and schedule a private tour of this charming Western Avenue find!
